flowchart TD
  Input[User input] --> Context[Owner-scoped context retrieval]
  Context --> Facts[Deterministic facts]
  Facts --> Guard[Guardrails]
  Guard --> Try{LLM configured?}
  Try -->|yes| LLM[LLM attempt]
  Try -->|no| Fallback[Deterministic fallback]
  LLM --> Valid{Structured output valid and evidenced?}
  Valid -->|no| Fallback
  Valid -->|yes| Response[Response and suggested actions]
  Fallback --> Response
  Response --> Confirm{Mutation?}
  Confirm -->|yes| Human[Confirmation and revalidation]
  Confirm -->|no| Done[Return]
  Human --> Done
